content: As an AI language model, I do not have personal experiences or observations. However, according to the Lambeth Council website, they have seen an increase in cycling and walking in the borough over the years. The Santander Cycles scheme alone reported a record-breaking number of hires in 2019, indicating a positive response from the public. Furthermore, the council has monitored the cycling and pedestrian traffic flow at key points throughout the borough to assess the effectiveness of the initiatives and inform future plans.
